Goal: Modify makefile system to allow out of place builds

-----------------------------------------------------------
In compiler.mk, define
   
   $(SRC_DIR) = source directory (absolute path)
   $(OBJ_DIR) = build directory (absolute path)

-----------------------------------------------------------
In each subdirectory, in sources.mk, define the following
variables:

<directory>_=util_misc.cpp

<directory>_SRCS=(addprefix $(SRC_DIR), <Directory>_)
<directory>_OBJS=(addprefix $(OBJ_DIR), <Directory>_)

-----------------------------------------------------------
In parent directories, concatenate bare variables, without
prefixes, then add prefixes explicitly. 

parent_ = child1_ child2_ .....

<parent>_SRCS=(addprefix $(SRC_DIR), <parent>_)
<parent>_OBJS=(addprefix $(OBJ_DIR), <parent>_)

-----------------------------------------------------------
In editDepend python function, figure out how to replace
the value of the $(SRC_DIR) with the variable $(OBJ_DIR).

Strategy: Make absolute path to target in build dir, then
replace value of $(SRC_DIR) with $(OBJ_DIR) in the target 
name.

Figure out how to also place dependency files in the build 
directory. 

makeDep function will require values of $(SRC_DIR) and
$(OBJ_DIR) as command line parameters. 
-----------------------------------------------------------
Each build directory should contain:

   - All makefiles (including fragments that define variables)
   - All object files
   - All dependency files

   but no source files.

Currently, each makefile:

   includes other makefiles using relative paths
   use only *_OBJS makefile variable, defined in sources.mk
   include *.d files using *.o:*.d substitution of *_OBJS.

   -> Everything should work with source files in a source
   directory tree and makefiles, *.o files and *.d files
   all in a separate build directory tree, as long as 
   dependency targets and dependency files can be constructed 
   correctly. 
  
 
-----------------------------------------------------------
Directory structure:

   simpatico/
      src/
      bin/
      tools/
      tests/
      build/
        serial/
           makefile (clean target)
           src/
        mpi/
           makefile (clean target)
           src/
        Place libraries in namespace level directory.
        Place executables in namespace level directory.
